query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT county) as unique_counties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CONCAT(county, '-', parcelId)) as unique_combos,
  COUNT(*) - COUNT(DISTINCT CONCAT(county, '-', parcelId)) as duplicates,
  MAX(createdAt) as latest_property_added
FROM properties;
